    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a dependable choice for someone looking for a functional daily driver. The exterior shows its age with some clear coat peeling on the trunk and a few minor door dings from regular use. Inside, the upholstery has some staining and the driver's seat shows significant bolster wear, though all electronics and climate controls remain fully operational. Mechanically, it runs well, but prospective buyers should expect to address some upcoming suspension maintenance and perhaps a set of new tires in the near future. It\u2019s an honest car that has been used regularly and is priced to reflect its current cosmetic and mechanical state.",
      "price": 18500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional automotive specimen, this vehicle arrives in flawless, showroom condition. Meticulously preserved and maintained to the highest standards, it offers a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that looks and drives exactly as it did the day it left the factory. From the pristine paintwork to the immaculate interior, every detail reflects a level of care that is seldom seen on the market. This is an investment-grade vehicle for the discerning buyer who demands nothing less than perfection. Experience the pinnacle of quality and performance in a package that remains indistinguishable from new.",
      "price": 48900.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly a bit heartbroken to be letting go of my absolute pride and joy. This beauty has been my weekend baby, kept tucked away in a climate-controlled garage and treated more like a family member than a machine. It\u2019s in truly stunning shape\u2014the kind of car that makes you look back every time you walk away. The paint still has that deep, showroom shine, and the interior smells just like it did on day one. It\u2019s been pampered with every service done right on time, so it runs like an absolute dream. If you\u2019re looking for a car that\u2019s been loved and cared for by someone who truly appreciates a fine ride, you\u2019ve found it. Come by for a coffee and a look; I\u2019d love to see it go to another enthusiast!",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered here is a mechanically superlative example, meticulously sorted for the enthusiast who values tactile feedback and engineering integrity. The powertrain features a blueprint-balanced rotating assembly with optimized thermal management, ensuring consistent performance even under high-load cycles. We\u2019ve eliminated drivetrain lash with upgraded subframe inserts and a precision-valved suspension setup that offers exceptional high-speed damping and roll-center correction. The throttle response is instantaneous, benefiting from a port-matched intake and a recalibrated ECU map that prioritizes a linear power band. This chassis exhibits zero torsional fatigue, and the undercarriage is as clean as the day it left the assembly line\u2014no weeping seals or heat-compromised components. Truly a turn-key machine for those who demand a factory-plus experience.",
      "price": 48950.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Showroom quality. Zero flaws. Mechanically perfect. Priced to move today.",
      "price": 43000.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Step into a time capsule of elegance and raw emotion. This isn't just a vehicle; it\u2019s a symphony of polished chrome and hand-stitched leather that whispers stories of coastal drives and sun-drenched afternoons. Every curve of its silhouette captures the light like a masterpiece in a gallery, promising a driving experience that transcends the mundane. When the engine stirs to life, it doesn't just run\u2014it breathes with a spirited heart that yearns for the open road. To own this is to possess a piece of history, a pristine companion that turns every errand into an event and every journey into a memory.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Experience the pinnacle of automotive excellence with this showroom-quality masterpiece. Meticulously maintained and preserved in pristine condition, this vehicle offers an uncompromising driving experience that feels indistinguishable from new. Every detail, from the flawless exterior finish to the untouched interior upholstery, reflects a standard of care rarely seen on the market. This is more than a car; it is a testament to precision engineering and dedicated stewardship. Secure a vehicle that represents the absolute gold standard in its class.",
      "price": 48900.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there, neighbor! I\u2019m finally ready to part with my absolute pride and joy. This beauty is in truly stunning shape\u2014honestly, it feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve babied this car from day one, keeping it tucked away and pristine; it\u2019s been my weekend treasure. It drives like an absolute dream and looks even better in person. Aside from maybe a tiny, barely-visible speck of character, she\u2019s as close to perfect as you\u2019re ever going to find. I\u2019d love for it to go to a fellow enthusiast who will appreciate it as much as I have. Come on over, let's chat cars, and take her for a spin!",
      "price": 44900.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously sorted E46 M3, a true driver\u2019s spec that has been maintained with an open checkbook. The S54 straight-six is in peak health, having undergone a full top-end refresh including Beisan VANOS seals and a comprehensive rod bearing service for total peace of mind. The chassis is rock-solid, featuring a reinforced rear subframe and a track-ready suspension setup utilizing KW V3 coilovers for surgical turn-in. Power delivery is immediate and linear, optimized by a custom ECU remap that eliminates the factory flat spots. Every mechanical interface, from the short-throw shifter to the high-durometer bushings, has been calibrated for maximum tactile feedback. This is a turn-key, investment-grade example that sounds as visceral as it drives. Serious inquiries only for this analog masterpiece.",
      "price": 49500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_8",
